{"tid":113244,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[iPhone專用] 等了又等！BeatsX藍牙耳機終於開賣","createTime":"2017-02-08T19:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T07:01:07.000Z","uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27af5932752ba1d816903d8c58be664a09bc3b55","tid":113244,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:03:07.000Z","msg":"Beats 推出全新後掛式藍牙無線耳機 BeatsX，並將於 2 月 10 日正式發售。詃系列除配備黑白兩款顏色外，也會於日後加推灰色和藍色。至於功能方面，由於採用 Apple 自家與 AirPod 相同的 W1 晶片，功能及操作大同小異。更重要的是藉 Beats 對音色表現的加持，音色質素也應勝過 AirPod，而且售價再平 AirPod HK$100，以 HK$1188 開售。<br />\n<br />\n全新 BeatsX 無線耳機，減輕了機身重量，讓佩戴時更覺輕盈舒適自在。此外，雖採用 Apple W1 晶片，但能與《iOS》 及《Android》系統對應。若用戶使用是 《iOS 10》系統 iPhone，BeatsX 更提供簡易藍牙連接，及能於 iCloud 註冊的裝置設備間無縫切換。<br />\n<br />\n另外，機內配備了  Fast Fuel 快速充電技術，通過隨機附送的 Lightning 充電線，5 分鐘充電即可連續播放 2 小時；充電 45分鐘更可提供長達 8 小時的電池電量。<br />\n<br />\n耳機線上的 RemoteTalk 功能除可接聽電話，播放音樂和啓動 Siri。Flex-Form 耳機線及可拆卸的耳翼，也可為用戶提供更靈活的佩戴方式，輕鬆掛在脖子上，防止打結。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oa0kf55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOa0kf55.jpg&h=83587fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到個b字都硬哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ac58523cd0b327d2a2bf389f2a7255c88f9d25","tid":113244,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:51:50.000Z","msg":"專用垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16eb8f334f5dc645c8b0b243ea4b16f83f57ebf9","tid":113244,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>專用垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊款無線耳筒高質過airpod同beatsX又做到差唔多價錢？"},{"pid":"6a057e85b959fdc32977a0bd7322698808d2c8b7","tid":113244,"uid":658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"w1 chip係個耳機定係條線度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係條線度想改裝落其他耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1ff8e420e73ede11878b0e12f8a3bf7203d6b5","tid":113244,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>專用垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊款無線耳筒高質過airpod同beatsX又做到差唔多價錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\njaybird"},{"pid":"80d6691657149e6a1c3d36aa879bb7c9e91b73d4","tid":113244,"uid":16923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:58:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>專用垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊款無線耳筒高質過airpod同beatsX又做到差唔多價錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\njaybird</blockquote><br />\njaybird x2"},{"pid":"6ffbd649da886a988e141adec936bb44d39137a7","tid":113244,"uid":19881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T07:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>專用垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊款無線耳筒高質過airpod同beatsX又做到差唔多價錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\njaybird</blockquote><br />\njaybird x2</blockquote><br />\njaybird x3 (Jaybird X3)"}]}